parameters.command:
=# -------- Parâmetros (n8n) --------
CHANNEL_ID="{{ $('@GLOBAL_ANCAPSU').item.json.CHANNEL_ID }}"
LAST_N_HOURS={{ $('@GLOBAL_ANCAPSU').item.json.LAST_N_HOURS || 24 }}
MIN_DURATION={{ $('@GLOBAL_ANCAPSU').item.json.MIN_DURATION || 182 }}
MAX_DURATION={{ $('@GLOBAL_ANCAPSU').item.json.MAX_DURATION || 1800 }}
N={{ $json.LIMIT || 50 }}

# -------- Cálculo do corte por epoch --------
NOW_EPOCH=$(date -u +%s)
CUTOFF_EPOCH=$(( NOW_EPOCH - LAST_N_HOURS*3600 ))

# -------- Lista filtrando por epoch, duração e disponibilidade pública --------
yt-dlp "https://www.youtube.com/channel/${CHANNEL_ID}/videos" \
  --skip-download \
  --ignore-errors \
  --no-abort-on-error \
  --no-warnings \
  --match-filter "availability = public & timestamp != None & duration != None & timestamp >= ${CUTOFF_EPOCH} & duration >= ${MIN_DURATION} & duration <= ${MAX_DURATION}" \
  --playlist-end "$N" \
  --print "%(id)s | %(title)s | %(duration_string)s | %(timestamp>%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S)s | %(webpage_url)s" \
  || true
